'''思高'''（英文：'''Scotch'''）是[[3M公司|3M公司]]的一个品牌，主要用于胶带产品和清洁产品上。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scotchbrand.com/wps/portal/3M/en_US/ScotchBrand/Scotch/Resources/History/?WT.mc_id=www.3M.com%2Fbrands%2Fscotch%2Fanniversary%2Fimages%2FScotchHistoryFinal.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-10-02 |archive-date=2015-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704180419/http://www.scotchbrand.com/wps/portal/3M/en_US/ScotchBrand/Scotch/Resources/History/?WT.mc_id=www.3M.com%2Fbrands%2Fscotch%2Fanniversary%2Fimages%2FScotchHistoryFinal.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
